Class SessionModel

java.lang.Object
splendor.view.SessionModel
public final class SessionModel extends Object
Models the session information needed by the LobbyPage.

  • Constructor Details

    • SessionModel

      public SessionModel(String sessionId, String creatorName, String players, boolean isLaunched, boolean isSaveGame, int playerCount)
      Create a new Session entry.
      Parameters:
      sessionId - sessionId of the session
      creatorName - username of the player that create the session
      players - list of all players in the session, including the creator
      isLaunched - boolean initialising the value of isLaunched
      isSaveGame - flag for if the session was created from a saved game or not.
      playerCount - Player count.
